                    "order": 1,
                    "type": "html",
                    "title": "Introduction to Python",
                    "content": {
                        "html": "<h2>Why Python?</h2><ul><li>Simple, readable syntax</li><li>Huge ecosystem (NumPy, Django, TensorFlow…)</li><li>Used in web dev, data science, automation, AI</li></ul><pre style=\"background:#f3f4f6;padding:1rem;border-radius:6px\"><code>print(\"Hello, World!\")\\nname = input(\"Your name: \")\\nprint(f\"Hello, {name}!\")</code></pre>",
                        "layout": "default"
                    }
                },
                {
